From Times Staff and Wire Reports 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Bird Medical Technologies Inc. announced the appointment of Robert T. Corbett 
as executive vice president.In this new position, Corbett, 50, will be 
responsible for dealing with strategic issues and other matters related to 
corporate growth. Most recently, Corbett was the managing partner of Crimson 
Capital Co., a private investment bank. Corbett has been been on the Palm 
Springs-based firm's board since 1991. Bird Medical manufactures and markets a 
broad line of respiratory care equipment and disposable products to hospitals 
and other health care providers worldwide. 
</P>
</TEXT>
