<TEXT>
<P>
 David J. Brotman has been elected vice chairman of RTKL Associates Inc., a 
leading architectural/engineering firm.Brotman is also managing director of the 
firm's Pacific Rim regional headquarters in Los Angles. He joined the firm in 
1975 and was elected to the board in 1989. In 1992 he was named executive vice 
president and appointed to the firm's executive management committee. 
</P>
