 COACH: RECORD AT SCHOOL Dick Hill: 0-0 03,20,05,05 RETURNING STARTERS OFF DEF 
6 2 04,26,05,05,05 TOP RETURNERS OFF DEF YR Art Bell, 5-9, 160 WR DB Sr. Sam 
Cureton, 6-0, 200 RB LB Sr. Adam Dodge, 6-3, 260 OL DL Sr. Willie Ford, 6-4, 
280 OL DL Sr. Markos Garza, 5-10, 175 RB LB Jr. Alex Gonzalez, 5-8, 155 RB DB 
Sr. Tim Irving, 6-3, 200 TE LB Sr. Ernie Korsvall, 6-0, 205 TE LB Sr. Andy 
Lauridsen, 6-3, 190 QB DB Sr. Greg Overton, 6-3, 230 OL DL Sr. George Perez, 
