YOUTH SHOT AFTER 2 GROUPS ARGUE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A 17-year-old Monterey Park boy was shot after an argument between two groups 
of youths Saturday night at a fast-food restaurant, authorities said. 
</P>
<P>
