THEY'RE BACK 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Arriving in stores Tuesday are the CD and video for "The 3 Tenors" concert at 
Dodger Stadium.No lineups before 6 a.m. (Just kidding.) And coming soon to a 
cable system near you: 
</P>
<P>
 The 3 Tenors Channel -- all tenors, all the time. (That's a joke too . . . 
well, as far as we know.) 
</P>
