a.m. to explain what it takes to be a volunteer tour guide. Those who sign on 
to become guides will attend a series of Tuesday morning training classes. The 
museum is at 307 Cliff Drive, Laguna Beach. (714) 494-3054 or (714) 494-8971. 
</P>
