<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA082994-0171 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 074309 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
August 29, 1994, Monday, Home Edition Correction Appended 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part C; Page 1; Column 2; Sports Desk 
</P>
